These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, juice, soy-milk, sprite, milk
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: disaster, epic, scientific, horror, sports
There are 5 different nationalities: australian, brazilian, mexican, canadian, american
5 different pets are kept: snake, horse, ferret, dog, fish
 1. the owner of the fish is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
 2. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
 3. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 4. the person drinking soy-milk is the person drinking soy-milk##1
 5. the owner of the snake is the person watching disaster movies##1
 6. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 7. the australian is on the left of the mexican##1
 8. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 9. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
11. the person drinking milk is between the brazilian and the person watching sports movies##2
12. the canadian is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
13. the american is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate        | juice | milk     | soy-milk   | sprite |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific     | epic      | horror | sports   | disaster    |
| Nationality   | canadian  | brazilian     | australian | mexican | american  |
| Pet           | horse | ferret      | fish     | dog   | snake     |

