.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: singing, fishing, magic-tricks, card-games, traveling
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: salsa, house, blues, rock, dubstep
There are 5 different nationalities: malaysian, nigerian, canadian, german, french
The people use 5 different means of transport: trike, train, ship, motorbike, jet-ski
 1. the person driving the jet-ski is in the middle##1
 2. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 4. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the nigerian##1
 5. the person driving the train is between the malaysian and the fan of dubstep##2
 6. the person driving the motorbike is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 7. the fan of salsa is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 8. the canadian is the fan of rock##1
 9. the canadian is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
10. the fan of blues is on the right of the fan of house##1
11. the canadian is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
12. the person driving the train is on the right of the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Hobby         | card-games | singing | traveling    | fishing  | magic-tricks    |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep    | house       | blues      | salsa | rock        |
| Nationality   | french   | nigerian     | malaysian    | german  | canadian     |
| Transport     | ship    | train | jet-ski | motorbike | trike |

