.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: reading, video-games, chess, writing, sudoku
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: disaster, satire, thriller, fantasy, mystery
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: folk, rock, indie, d&b, house
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: lacrosse, ice-hockey, skiing, parkour, cricket
 1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the fan of rock##1
 2. the person who's sport is parkour is in the middle##1
 3. the fan of d&b is in the middle##1
 4. the person watching disaster movies is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 6. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the fan of folk##1
 7. the fan of house is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 8. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
 9. the fan of indie is on the far left##1
10. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person watching fantasy movies##1
11. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
12. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the fan of house##1
13. the person who's sport is cricket is between the person watching mystery movies and the person who's hobby is chess##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Hobby         | reading | sudoku     | chess   | video-games   | writing |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery  | satire | disaster | fantasy | thriller        |
| Music-Genre   | indie      | rock      | d&b       | house       | folk       |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | cricket  | parkour    | lacrosse    | skiing        |

