 3. the person eating apple is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
 4. the turkish is between the fan of trance and the person eating cabbage##2
 5. the person eating apple is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 6. the fan of r&b is on the right of the dutch##1
 7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person eating peas##1
 8. the person who's hobby is hiking is the fan of disco##1
 9. the fan of r&b is in the middle##1
10. the fan of trance is the canadian##1
11. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
12. the canadian is on the right of the fan of folk##1
13. the fan of disco is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
