.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-5::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite, fanta, 7up, cola
There 5 different types of food: raspberry, garlic, lime, pear, banana
The people have 5 different jobs:  architect, project-manager, musician, bartender, chef
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: basketball, water-polo, badminton, biathlon, snowboarding
 1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the architect##1
 2. the person eating pear is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 3. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 4. the person drinking fanta is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person eating raspberry##2
 5. the person eating banana is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 6. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person eating pear##1
 7. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the project-manager##1
 8. the chef is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 9. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the architect##1
11. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person eating lime##1
12. the bartender is on the left of the architect##1
13. the person eating lime is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |       2       |       3       |       4       |    5     |
| Beverage   | 7up       | cola       | hot-chocolate   | fanta      | sprite    |
| Food       | banana | pear        | raspberry       | lime       | garlic |
| Job        | chef     | project-manager        | bartender | architect        | musician  |
| Sport      | biathlon | badminton | basketball      | snowboarding | water-polo  |

