 3. the owner of the chinchilla is the person driving the jet-ski##1
 4. the owner of the bird is between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the british##2
 5. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 6. the person who's hobby is camping is in the middle##1
 7. the japanese is on the right of the malaysian##1
 8. the dutch is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the goldfish is the japanese##1
10. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person driving the car##1
11. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the malaysian##1
12. the owner of the hedgehog is the person who's hobby is reading##1
13. the owner of the bird is on the left of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |     4      |      5       |
