 5. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 7. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 8. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
 9. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
10. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far left##1
11. the person driving the taxi is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2
12. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
13. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Beverage    | lemonade       | tea    | almond-milk | sprite  | water        |
| Hobby       | board-games | chess | magic-tricks  | skydiving | gardening    |
| Sport       | snowboarding        | tennis   | swimming  | volleyball   | cycling |
| Transport   | boat       | taxi      | skateboard      | jet-ski | snowmobile  |

