.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, almond-milk, hot-chocolate, tea, fanta
The people have 5 different jobs:  chef, designer, social-worker, writer, teacher
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: family, time-travel, martial-arts, sports, western
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: jazz, reggae, r&b, funk, punk
 1. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 2. the writer is between the person watching martial-arts movies and the social-worker##2
 3. the person drinking tea is the writer##1
 4. the person watching western movies is on the right of the fan of funk##1
 5. the person watching family movies is in the middle##1
 6. the person drinking tea is between the teacher and the fan of reggae##2
 7. the fan of funk is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 8. the person drinking soy-milk is the fan of r&b##1
 9. the fan of jazz is on the left of the teacher##1
10. the chef is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
11. the social-worker is the person watching time-travel movies##1
12. the person watching sports movies is on the far left##1
13. the person drinking fanta is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
