5 different pets are kept: pony, snake, frog, hamster, rabbit
The people use 5 different means of transport: skateboard, boat, van, motorbike, snowmobile
 1. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
 2. the malaysian is on the left of the russian##1
 3. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 4. the person driving the van is on the far left##1
 5. the owner of the snake is between the spanish and the owner of the pony##2
 6. the spanish is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the person driving the skateboard and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
 8. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is boatd-games##2
 9. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the person who's hobby is boatd-games##1
10. the person who's hobby is boatd-games is on the right of the australian##1

