The people prefer 5 different music-genres: metal, techno, d&b, salsa, folk
There are 5 different nationalities: indonesian, colombian, italian, dutch, mexican
 1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
 2. the person watching family movies is between the dutch and the fan of folk##2
 3. the fan of folk is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 4. the person watching family movies is the fan of metal##1
 5. the fan of metal is between the mexican and the fan of d&b##2
 6. the mexican is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 7. the person watching disaster movies is the fan of salsa##1
 8. the person who's hobby is folk-climbing is the fan of techno##1
 9. the indonesian is the fan of techno##1
10. the person who's hobby is folk-climbing is on the right of the italian##1
11. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
12. the person watching animation movies is on the far left##1

